Annotations @
Priority

*annotations we should always define a method non static 
1. @Test  -- Testcase
2. @Before Test -- Pre condition
3. @After Test -- Post Condition
4. @Before Method -- Condition runs before Pre & Test
5. @AfterMethod -- Condition runs after Test and before Post
6. @BeforeClass -- 
7. @AfterClass --
8. @DataProvider -- Supplies data 
9. @BeforeSuite -- 
10.@AfterSuite --

